⚡ **Features**:
- Single cells, shrinkage
- NO inflammation
- ATP-dependent
- Membrane intact (blebs)

🔵 **Intrinsic Pathway**:
DNA damage → p53 → BAX/BAK → MOMP → Cytochrome c → Apoptosome → Caspase-9 → Caspase-3

🔴 **Extrinsic Pathway**:
FasL + Fas → DISC → Caspase-8 → Caspase-3

🔬 **BCL-2 Family**:
