📊 **Leukocyte Extravasation**:
1. Margination
2. Rolling (Selectins: E, P, L)
3. Adhesion (Integrins: LFA-1, Mac-1)
4. Transmigration (PECAM-1)
5. Chemotaxis (C5a, LTB4, IL-8)

⚡ **Respiratory Burst**:
NADPH oxidase → O₂⁻ → H₂O₂ → HOCl

🦠 **CGD Organisms**: Catalase +ve
**SAAN-B**: Staph, Aspergillus, Serratia, Nocardia, Burkholderia`,
