1. Hemostasis/Inflammation (0-3d)
2. Proliferation (3-14d)
3. Remodeling (weeks-year)

⚡ **Key Factors**:
- VEGF: Angiogenesis
- TGF-β: Fibrosis
- Vitamin C: Collagen hydroxylation
- Zinc: Epithelialization

📈 **Wound Strength**:
- Week 1: 10%
- Month 3: 70-80%
- Never >80%`,
